snippet.title: South Park: The Stick of Truth E3 Official Trailer
snippet.description: From the perilous battlefields of the fourth-grade playground, a young hero will rise, destined to be South Park's savior. From the creators of South Park, Trey Parker and Matt Stone, comes an epic quest to become... cool. Introducing South Park: The Stick of Truth.  Coming to XBox 360, PS3 and PC on March 5, 2013
